commitResults.messageTitle: Level-0: Added Rename,Greet,Exit and Changed Duke to MeowTheCat
Level-1: Echos commands entered by the user, and exits when the user types the command bye
Level-2: Add ability to store and list user-entered tasks. Implemented 'list' command to display all stored tasks. Also allowed adding of tasks to list.

Level-3: Level 3: Add ability to mark tasks as done or not done Implemented 'mark' and 'unmark' commands to update task completion status. Updated task display format to show [X] for done and [ ] for not done. Introduced a Task class to encapsulate task data and behavior.
